bahawa jika dia menyerang awak

237
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:23,240
semasa awak bawah umur 14 tahun,

238
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:26,039
tanpa mengira persetujuan awak, ia dikira rogol,

239
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:26,919
betul?

240
00:12:30,519 --> 00:12:31,879
Ya, tapi...

241
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:33,240
Semasa awak bercakap tadi,

242
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,320
awak berulang kali menggunakan

243
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:36,600
istilah bertulis seperti "serangan".

244
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,519
Jadi awak tahu undang-undang

245
00:12:37,519 --> 00:12:39,279
dan unsur-unsur

246
00:12:39,279 --> 00:12:41,840
yang membentuk kes rogol, betul?

247
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:46,159
Saya belajar sedikit daripada manual undang-undang.

